videos.description: Texas Tech's Tariq Owens cuts off the pick and roll and slams home the lob from Matt Mooney over a defender.
videos.headline: Owens posterizes defender off the lob

videos.description: Lindy Waters III splits two defenders and gets the last second 3-pointer up to send the game into overtime.
videos.headline: Waters nails buzzer beater to force OT
